<div class="img-container"><a href="/women/2010/october/best-christian-halloween-party.html"><img class="img-container_item" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/84177.jpg?w=220" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/84177.jpg?w=440 2x" width="220" alt="The Best Christian Halloween Party" title="The Best Christian Halloween Party" /></a></div>
<div class="slug uppercase spacer-top-10"><a href="/women/opinion/">Opinion</a><span class="seprator"> | </span>Pop Culture</div>
<a class="title title-3 js-editableItem" href="/women/2010/october/best-christian-halloween-party.html" alt="" title="" data-type="article" data-id="100234">The Best Christian Halloween Party</a><span class="lock-image"><img width="10" height="12" src="/system/img/icon_lock.svg" alt="Subscriber access only" title="Subscriber access only" /></span><div class="deck spacer-top-5">Along with hell houses and harvest fests, might evangelicals consider celebrating All Saints' Day?</div>
